How would one say "over the past few weeks/days"?
by Sivak » Fri 05.15.2009 1:09 am Well, topic pretty much says it all.But if I wanted to say the following, how would I do it?Over the past few weeks...Over the past few days...For the past month or so...I had a guess for this situation:"For the past two weeks or so..."略２週は。。。 though I'm probably wrong.Thank you for any information!
Sivak
Posts: 20Joined: Fri 05.01.2009 6:24 pm
Native language: English
