Re: How would one say "over the past few weeks/days"?
by Yudan Taiteki » Fri 05.15.2009 2:32 pm Sivak wrote:I was wondering if this could also be interpreted as "have been studying"No, it cannot be interpreted that way. You will probably learn about -te iru later.
-Chris Kern
